    rg2.Rmd

    Parameters

    There are 3 types of parameters for rg2:

    1. aesthetic mapping
    2. plot style
    3. cfg

    cfg parameter in rg2 is a object of list, a full supported options document: G2Plot API

    Example

    a basic example

    ggplot2::economics_long %>% 
  filter(variable %in% c('psavert', 'uempmed')) %>% 
  g2Line(date, value, seriesField = variable)
